tweets.text:
🌶️ 🥒  A spicy, not so cool seizure. 

@CBPSouthTexas found $930K of cocaine in a shipment of cucumbers &amp; jalapeños. After a nonintrusive inspection, followed by a physical inspection,  70lbs of drugs were found concealed within a tractor trailer.

➡️ https://t.co/sib6CXPSxJ https://t.co/EN1ReJwNE1

